added.description: Babs and Buster are excited to get college jobs, but can they stand the heat cooking for the school chef?

added.description: Buster finds a cloning machine at Wile E. Coyote's yard sale that he uses to make another Buster and Babs and Sweetie snag a time machine that they use to open a vintage clothing store.

added.description: When Thomas builds an obstacle course for his friends, he gets upset when they won't play with it HIS way.

added.title: The Floor is Grape Jelly
added.description: When David is frustrated to be called home early to help with his baby sister, Barney creates a magical game where David is reminded how good it feels to help others. He leaves the park excited to help out as a big brother.

added.title: I Lovey You
added.description: Barney's magic creates a nighttime adventure in the park, but David is scared of the dark. Barney becomes a giant glowing action figure to help David calm down so he can stay and play with his friends.

added.title: Mel's Greatest Treasure
added.description: Mel is on a quest to find a special treasure and accidentally makes a big mess in the park. Barney creates a magical adventure where Mel learns it's important to clean up and care for a place that's special to you and your community.

added.title: One Ripe Tomato
added.description: When Vivie disagrees with her friends about who gets to use a ripe garden tomato, Barney creates space for everyone to share their ideas. Vivie realizes it's important to share and they use the tomato to make a pizza everyone can enjoy.

added.title: Spellbound
added.description: Witch Hazel hires The Looney Builders to make her house look spooky for Halloween, but things get complicated when they use her off-limits magical things.
